text: Esmaeil Jabbarzadeh (, 1960 â€“ 16 February 2022) was an Iranian politician. He was Governor of East Azerbaijan, Iran from 2013 to 2017. He won a seat from Tabriz for parliament in Iranian legislative elections of 1992, 1996, 2000, and 2004. He was a member of the Executives of Construction Party. Jabbarzadeh died from cardiac arrest on 16 February 2022. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Deaths from cardiac arrest Category:Iranian politicians
